Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和酷一行人同行的菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.79,0:02:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在ChaosChoir的命令下\N為離間酷和蕾而接近他們的間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功的話就能成為煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是她多年的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不知不覺間菲蘿真的喜歡上了酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.69,0:02:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而蕾也對心中所萌發的前所未有的感覺不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.20,0:02:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九唱 碎石的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 以及其他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 把你吵醒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續兩天星夜趕路實在是撐不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以正在做住宿的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這車子也是用了二十年的半淘汰品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像也很吃不消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算是搭好了 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧了我們的努力 對吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 一切都是菲蘿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 等等 沾在臉上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 你醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我過去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一個人待一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我想單獨待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想和酷在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會感覺很熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得啊 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然也下廚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶兒也動動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可能在約會什麼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來 怎麼做呢 菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,步驟就請問龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說這個 是說酷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動了真情可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初可能是為了別的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別隱瞞了 別隱瞞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初只是Fan和偶像的關係就很心滿意足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是說那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是酷很單純或者該說是很純真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有時也很想好好疼愛他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅說的是另一種意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可愛がる有两种意思，一是疼爱，二是严加管教{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 以後再也不說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷和蕾又沒有結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戀愛是自由的 盡情去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好吧 說這麼不負責任的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不要留下遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你已跟蕾一樣是我們的同伴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同伴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去打水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越想越不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你的便 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不顧別人的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去打水 陪我一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.22,0:06:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次同契的時候我自出生以來第一次感覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同步的和諧感什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次的時候我也感覺非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說呢 就像飛機機翼一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好高興啊 這就是默契吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷覺得誰更好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那個 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼問的話我也不知該怎麼答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況我覺得菲蘿和蕾各有各的優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是體貼啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事 我只是實話實說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽你這麼說我精神好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為一起旅行的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為什麼會說出那些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱熱的 不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後還是說不上話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不行啊 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃...吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果完全沒機會和蕾說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會討厭我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰好像很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就差一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.45,0:09:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個同契者和蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯的心正在疏遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就差一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.59,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼 照這樣子下去完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功之後你就能成為煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.51,0:09:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時就能和你那塊破石頭說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太接近煌珠樂園了變得更容易疲勞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.74,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概正睡得香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是累了正睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.25,0:10:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在這裏我能做個普通的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲蘿那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然萌發了不必要的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯 不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到了一個好點子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 可以讓我來做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙大人的狀態也不容樂觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事態緊急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩鬧也要適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用那女孩一舉將蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯從酷德身邊分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拐彎抹角的 這可不是遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敗的話就拋棄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正是有缺陷的破石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懸架以及其它一些部件都好像出現了鬆動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也許得花上一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.09,0:11:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們去找點食物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這是技術活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.66,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這也不像是小姐干的活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們兩人出去一會兒行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.23,0:11:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到離這不遠有處清澈的泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和蕾加深友誼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.27,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我借你泳衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.42,0:11:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過反正也沒人看到 裸體也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裸 裸體...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臉紅什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說在幻想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇雅 我們也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護那兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等 等等 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 好清澈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡你們也來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泳衣還有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為要看守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.89,0:12:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說你也不會游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且菲蘿的泳裝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的胸部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想其實不用躲起來換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過下意識地就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 最近狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟往常一樣精神滿滿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.86,0:13:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神滿滿的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾 快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像有話要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼守護翼會變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這又是個本質問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不由自主地就在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲蘿很開朗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛懂事的年齡就被改造成擬煌珠應該是很悲慘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼啊 一下子 我可不會游泳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那很淺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什 什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.34,0:14:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲蘿的核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡會說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明不像蕾那樣的完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡那顏色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾喜歡酷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是戀人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣算是戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個比如說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做過接吻什麼之類的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不是戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 我也非常喜歡酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.74,0:15:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我成為他的戀人你沒意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.19,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果酷沒意見的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 你別埋怨我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷可能也覺得還是菲蘿好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得漂亮 菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好吃的 這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 好兆頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個怎麼弄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能吃的話怎麼都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 多吃點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過在我們這麼歡笑期間不知敵人會什麼時候來襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.35,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放心 那個時候我和酷會把他們打得落花流水的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.26,0:16:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 和菲蘿合作一下子就能搞定 沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來 快點吃完繼續做剩下的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能過來一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 稍微失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨 小菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿京娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去和酷德結婚的話我會祝福你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.76,0:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯的力量讓你成為煌珠之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你舉行一個盛大的結婚典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.14,0:17:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你送去一匹刺客要好好利用加深和酷的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我 和酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 為了這個而苦惱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.86,0:17:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為什麼突然說討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和蕾說話才想和她獨處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛啊 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是很認真地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是酷 你之前不是說過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.68,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾要是多少吃點醋就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是說過 那又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾的那種態度怎麼想都是在吃醋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概對蕾來說也是潛意識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道怎麼做才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不願和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得是 大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.27,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菲蘿
