Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏了啊 我找了半天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.92,0:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
