Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是從哪兒冒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.83,0:19:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 我們一起...
